Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People or heirlooms—that is the question, \Nor so it would sound if this was Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The furious Count gets {\i1}this{\i0} close \Nto making good on his vow to slice Benio open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,With his wits and good timing, \NShinobu deescalates the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Benio's already fed up. She bids farewell to everyone and leaves of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,For once, the Count's stubbornness is met with condemnation from his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu is chosen to be the messenger, \Nsent after Benio to bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my leave then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Benio is not out of the woods yet, as her strict father is not happy with her latest escapade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why I gave you this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is deplorable! \NYou've gravely offended the lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I may say a word, \Nit is Shinobu who is deplorable!{情けないのは 伊集院少尉の方なんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise that womanizer!{あんな女ったらし大嫌い}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Womanizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Every day, our mail was flooded with piles this big, all love letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's that geisha from Yanagibashi he's really close with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Geisha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. On top of that, she's even prettier than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that someone like him would do such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you trust my words, Father?{お父様は私の言うこと信じないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! An imperial soldier would not stoop so low \Nas to indulge in that kind of behaviour!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying {\i1}soldier this, soldier that{\i0}. You really think soldiers are all heavenly beings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't slam the table at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call what you're doing right now?!{Then why do you keep slamming it?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare slander the army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you trust just about anyone \Nover your own daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up!{黙れ黙れ黙れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like father, like daughter...{やっぱり親子そっくり}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Benio...{紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My one and only Benio...{僕だけの紅緒さんたった一人の}
