Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What are you doing?{何すんのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please don't hurt me!{乱暴をよして}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to be more discrete.{You need to be careful too.} {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father and daughter finally arguing again—\Njust let them work it out between themselves. {in their own pace}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably take them a while \Nafter all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ma'am, a lovely father-daughter quarrel is on again for the first time in a while.} Ma'am, you are hearing the lovely sounds of a fresh father-daughter quarrel.
