Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.15,Top,,0,0,0,,You're still the daughter of a soldier!{それでも軍人の娘だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.03,Top,,0,0,0,,I'm your daughter!{私はお父様の娘ですよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:08.98,Top,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.37,Top,,0,0,0,,{私の娘---impossible to get what they're saying}What? Didn't you say you're no daughter of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the people in this family seem to enjoy their arguments a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.21,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{impossible to get what they're saying}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:15.92,Top,,0,0,0,,I don't remember saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.38,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{impossible to get what they're saying}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.21,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice evening.{いい晩だな}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:23.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to this commotion really makes me feel at home.{あの騒ぎを聞いてるとしみじみ我が家へ帰っ たって気がするぜおや}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if it isn't Ushi.\NJust in time, I need you to take me somewhere.{ushiさんじゃないかちょうどよかった頼むよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't want to go anywhere tonight.{あしゃね今夜ここ動きたくねえんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.51,Top,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! I'm busy listening to the soothing melody \Nof this father-daughter quarrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.57,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.53,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't make up silly excuses!{バカなことを言いてないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, give me a lift, \NI'll give you a good tip.{さ出してくれ下がっては弾むから}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, up we go.\NThere, you can start going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You still can't understand?!{これだけ言ってもまだわからんのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:56.25,Overlap,,0,0,0,,{わからないのはお父様の方です}You're the one who can't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you defying your father?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ken, it's been a while.{あら、けんさん、しばらく}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just "a while"—you've neglected us completely. There hasn't been a lesson in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put yourself in our shoes!{あたしたちの身にもなってくださいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, my bad,{悪い悪い}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've simply been too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you're beautiful as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, when will we rehearse?{ねねねおさらいはいつから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait. \NNo need to rush things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going anywhere anytime soon, \Nso we'll have plenty of time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.02,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be rehearsing this month \Naccording to our normal schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!{もちろんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must get in touch with the theater at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them a call.{お電話しといて}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must get our costumes ready too!{それから衣装の準備もしなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll leave it to you.{お願い任せるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!{はいはい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Master, since we're all finally reunited tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't we celebrate it with some pomp \Nand sake on the side?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.{いいわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can you go get some takeout\Nand buy drinks from the liquor store?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, Young Master!{若師匠、若師匠}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what is it?{あらどうだった}
