Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 19
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 191
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1911
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1911.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1911..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1911...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Theatre was opened in 1911...{/44th year of meiji - 帝国劇場は明治44年に開場された。。。 - I'm not really sure what's the point}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell are you waiting for?{\i0}{何をぐずぐずしておるのや}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't Benio your fiancée?{\i0}{べにおはお前の許婚ではないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then go bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\blur1\c&HA49EA6&\3c&H4E4759&\pos(529.89,34.4)}Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen, watch your step!{印念中佐足元が}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk! Not drunk at all!{from the italian version - also gotta be some pun with the previous line}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we warn you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Colonel​?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to tumble after a little alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To the next bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to yer watering hole{stomping ground} this time, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir! Please let me show the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A horse! I wanna ride that horse! \NStop that fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you can't be serious! \NThat'd be unlawful! {lit: innen tsukero = are you inventing a pretext to pick a fight?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am serious. \NAnd don't call me Shirley. {had to rewatch Airplane to come up with this}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's Second Lieutenant Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What, Ijuuin?{何伊集院}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ijuuin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme your horse! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yikes.{あーまずい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop there!{止まれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme your horse!{そのお任せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go!{よし行くぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that any way to treat your superior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How insolent!{無礼者}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,An officer can't behave like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget about the chain of command, \Nyou moron?!{軍人直営を忘れだかバカ者}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oy-oy-oy...{ありゃありゃありゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't this where we started?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi! Aren't we circling around the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell ya that I don't wanna leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's best that I get off this wild ride? {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your pampered upbringing \Nthat you lack the necessary patience now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I have plenty of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of man Ijuuin Jr. is, as his bride, you must dedicate every ounce of patience to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden Bat paper roll cigarettes\Nwent on the market about ten years prior, in 1906,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and cost four {\i1}sen{\i0} per 10-pack. {of ten}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,At home you obey your parents; as a wife, \Nyou obey your husband; and as an old lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you obey your sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the line of thought that the women and children of Japan must abide by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so old-fashioned, Father.{古い、古い、お父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to the mansion. \NIjuuin Jr. must be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... This anachronism is inherent to my own family as well as to the Ijuuins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you don't care what ordeals \NI'm having to go through?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a woman leaves her home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she shall never set foot in it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Period! No objections! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And never coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lady Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing that you'd probably want to celebrate\Nand have a lavish feast tonight, I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if I should boil some white noodles. {no clue whats saka here}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get to taste your noodles \Never again, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why so?{どうしたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got kicked out. \NFrom this house as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What are you saying?{なんですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait just a second!{ちょっと待ってくださいますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always have to end up like this?{このうちの人はすぐこうなんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, don't be so hasty!{いいですか早まっちゃいけません}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear, there was nothing else I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for her own sake \Nthat I'm sending her back to the Ijuuins'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean? \NAren't you the one being hasty here? {/why are you in such a hurry}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... B-But weren't you about to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take me for a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With a daughter like Benio, no amount of lives is enough if you kill yourself after each of her escapades.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.{それもそうですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! How insulting! \NAlright, if this is the way it has to be...{なんたる侮辱よしこうなったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll not see me ever again! {lit: definitely leave of my own accord}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My young lady, please stop it...{お嬢様やめてくださいます}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, take care, Nanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And take care of Father, okay?{お父様のこと 頼むわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Master,{ねえねえ若師匠}\Nit's been a long time, hasn't it?{本当久しぶりね}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you?{どこ行ってたんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the feast is ready, and we have a solid plan for next month's performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,won't you make a toast, Master?{ね若師匠乾杯の音頭をとってくださいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then. \NLet's raise our glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to everyone's health, to the actors of Fujieda School,\Nand to the success of our next spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!{乾杯}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord!{大変}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is terrible!{大変なのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, what happened, Nanny? \NYou look dismayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The young lady has fled the house again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop her, Ranmaru!{止めてranmaruさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a disaster! I gotta go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone, I'm leaving!{じゃあ皆さん失礼するわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?{ええ何ですって}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about next month's show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just gonna have to do it without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I already booked the theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had already ordered the costumes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And think of all this food going to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, then. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Master...{ちょっと若師匠ったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at a loss...{俺だからもう}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't actually mean \Nto take Ranmaru away from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to stop Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!{待って}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, to hell with it! \NI can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? He thinks he can order me around just cos he's a soldier? {nanisa, gunjin gunjin to ibarunatte}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm coming here ever again! \NI regret nothing, you rotten dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait! \NWe can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady!{お嬢様}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's gone...{いっちまった}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi! It's bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nanny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The young lady and Ranmaru have run away from home again! Hurry up and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! That means Boss needs me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, this is your stop. \NGimme my tip and get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've not moved me one inch from where I got on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have the nerve to ask for a tip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No refunds... {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And off you go! {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord...{旦那様}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I might've gone a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You really didn't have to bring it to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We went too far, it's hard to know when to stop with her. {lit: the medicine worked too well, because measuring just the right amount is difficult with her}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy to see Benio back myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, I know that for her own good \Nshe must return to the Ijuuins' mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What could that be?{/can it be...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!{ごめんください}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So he came for her after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for the late visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Hanamura,{花村少佐殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened today was the result \Nof my own indecision. {no idea what he means by itarazu, maybe "indecisiveness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't solely your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Benio here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Hasn't she come back to your place yet?{紅緒はまだ君の家に戻っておらんのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I mean she left for your place a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She must not have arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She only left a short while ago, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'll need to use your telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello, please put me through \Nto the Ijuuin residence in Otowadai.{otowadai is in kyoto so it couldn't possibly be there but idk and idc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss, this is the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't go to the Count's mansion.{こっち行ったんじゃ伯爵家は遠回りで}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said we're going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.{あそうじゃあ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, in the event that Benio returns, \Ntake her to her room and let her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back shortly. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, don't worry. She's got to be going there. \NShe's got nowhere else to return to. {no clue what he means: あれのことだ、帰りにいくくてその辺にいるのだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll check any places she may have gone on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir. Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Say, Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{You see, Benio told me about a certain... \Ngeisha from Yanagibashi, or something like that.}\NYou see, Benio told me that in Yanagibashi she encountered a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,geisha, or someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, if that's what this is about, I assure you \Nthere's no cause for concern, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought. \NI'm glad I never doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio jumped to conclusions without consulting me and kept silent about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to talk to her about it once I get a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be leaving.{では失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of her.{あれをよろしく頼む}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how difficult she can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!{とんでもありません}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio turned out to be just the kind \Nof person I thought her to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, I sometimes think \Nthat I'm not worthy of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Benio, what are we going to do?{ねぇBenioさんどうするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a minute, I'm trying to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been thinking for a while, haven't you?{さっきからずっと考えてるじゃない}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know I've slammed the door in both houses now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back to either.{どっちも戻れないでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to return home, after all the stuff I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I've also had just about enough of that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it always end up like this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of it.{自分で嫌なっちゃうわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, Boss Benio, \Nhow about we use this occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to go somewhere festive,\Nwith lots of drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! That's a great{grand} idea!\NI was also considering drowning this affair in drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio can't control herself when drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can go home on your own.{じゃああんただけ一人で言えよ帰り}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I don't deserve this treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, let's go!{Ushigorou, さ 行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Lessgo, lessgo! \NC'mon, Ushigorou, lessgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Abuse after abuse...\NWhy is it always me? {/do I have to bear this alone?} {/why is it always just me}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can keep you company!{私がついてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Shinobu? \NThat womanizer...{少尉が何するあの女たらし}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, Father also took his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking can fix anything! \NPour me another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Sorry for the wait.{はいお待ちどうさま}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Another one!{じゃんじゃん行こう}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Boss!{さすが親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi! Don't make her drink any more!{うしさんべにおさんに飲ませるはいい加減にして}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Alcohol is the broom that sweeps away sorrow! {https://andmorefine.com/en/proverbs/sake-drives-away-grief-dustpan} {Alcohol is the broom that sweeps sadness out!} {literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw Shinobu, screw Father,\Nscrew all the soldiers, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Col, are we leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't speak nonsense. We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to take a leak. {could be "I'm just a bit tipsy." but that doesn't explain where he's going}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!{ちょっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on something.{何か踏んづけたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! \NHow dare you do this to a soldier's headwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier? What of it if you're a soldier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got the drunken eyes. {目が据ってる - glazed eyes - not sure if this is really what you say about the drunken look}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,T-T-This is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin's a soldier. \NFather's a soldier too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's this nasty guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bitch, you're talking to the imperial soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect to achieve \Nwith a sword that blunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious saber...{わしの大切なサーベルが。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers this, soldiers that... \NIt's nuffin' to be proud of!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our high collar lady is dauntless,\Nbut she had chosen a dangerous opponent this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as this man is none other than Shinobu's superior,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and holds the lieutenant's fate wholly in his claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But well, they say ignorance is bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also true that no one knows what the future holds, \Nbut no one does it quite like our High Collar Lady. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Imperial Army is no match \Nfor blooming Benio in a drunken frenzy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so she mops the floor with five grown men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Boss is in danger!" - \NUshigorou dashes out to call for reinforcements,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shinobu gets bogged down in another brawl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,while the changed Count \Nfights the public nuisance with all his might. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio's surely incurred a lot of grievances tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0} "Scoring Grudges is Dangerous!"{恨み買いますご用心}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
